---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<h1 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-10 tracking-tight">Cascading Labs</h1>

	<p class="mb-6 font-light text-zinc-400">
		We are building the future of data and algorithms.
	</p>

	<p class="mb-6 font-light text-zinc-400">
		We aren't fully sure what that means yet, but we have the following assumptions:
	</p>

	<ul class="mb-6 pl-5 text-zinc-400 list-disc marker:text-slate-500">
		<li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Black-box AI is universally dumb.</li>
		<li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Knowledge is the impetus of action.</li>
		<li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Causality is too complicated.</li>
		<li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Fact checkers are necessarily biased.</li>
		<li class="mb-2 pl-2 font-light">Knowledge is a virus, and it spreads.</li>
	</ul>

	<div class="mt-14 flex gap-2 -ml-2">
		<a 
			href="https://github.com/CascadingLabs" 
			class="text-slate-500 no-underline px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-500/15"
		>
			GitHub
		</a>
	</div>
</Layout>
